  "detailed_description": "You're a dirty scallywag with nothing to lose. Dirty Dirty Pirates is a fast-paced, chaotic, player versus player fighting game, where fast reflexes and improvisation will help you become victorious. Stab, throw, roll, dance, mount, catch, and smash your way through frenzied battles in a looped battleground and enjoy the hilarious brutality.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LOCAL-MULTIPLAYER MAYHEM</strong></h2>Brawl with 2-8 players in a top down, blood-soaked, pirate battleground not for the faint of heart. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/2668caa01de89047245ffeab8088d502.poster.avif?t=1723566693\" width=640 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/2668caa01de89047245ffeab8088d502.webm?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/2668caa01de89047245ffeab8088d502.mp4?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHAOTIC LOOPED BATTLEGROUND</strong></h2>You and your thrown weapons wrap around the level, creating chaotic ways to slay your enemies (or yourself)!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/d04cf97ecafed6026899d84f298df6f0.poster.avif?t=1723566693\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/d04cf97ecafed6026899d84f298df6f0.webm?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/d04cf97ecafed6026899d84f298df6f0.mp4?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>POUNCE AND EXECUTE</strong></h2>Mount a downed pirate and choose your killing method. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/287cc37ec4fc1d005989b005479ee1fb.poster.avif?t=1723566693\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/287cc37ec4fc1d005989b005479ee1fb.webm?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/287cc37ec4fc1d005989b005479ee1fb.mp4?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GRATIFYING KILL CAMS</strong></h2>Watch the final kill of the match in slow motion and celebrate the brutality.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/6c4640a862cd00fd9b74db6a174dc6e8.poster.avif?t=1723566693\" width=640 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/6c4640a862cd00fd9b74db6a174dc6e8.webm?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/6c4640a862cd00fd9b74db6a174dc6e8.mp4?t=1723566693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WEAPONS WITH A MIND OF THEIR OWN</strong></h2><br>Not only are the weapons pointy and eager to impale – but they follow you! Better hide, catch, or roll, ya buccaneer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SLAUGHTER IN DIVERSE LANDS</strong></h2><br>Slay your foes at ship docks, ancient jungle ruins, desert, caves, and icy tundras.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE THE CHAOS</strong></h2><br>Reduce or increase the blood/gore to your liking (or disable it). Color blind mode is available as well. <br><br>Please note: This is a local multiplayer game without online gameplay. For the best experience, find a comfy couch and some friendly mateys in the same room or with Steam Remote Play.",
